        <type>void *</type>
        <definition>typedef void* sensing_sensor_handle_t</definition>
        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>sensing_sensor_handle_t</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Opaque handle to an opened sensor instance. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>A valid handle is obtained from <ref refid="group__sensing__api_1ga8e427d28efc492f15d762af3308d78cd" kindref="member">sensing_open_sensor</ref> or <ref refid="group__sensing__api_1ga4218453664fee0aa61697018e3193e7a" kindref="member">sensing_open_sensor_by_dt</ref> and must be closed with <ref refid="group__sensing__api_1ga98e49ea0e84e93867df20033d01ee66c" kindref="member">sensing_close_sensor</ref> when no longer needed. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
