</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>cb_list</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>callback list to be registered to sensing, must have a static lifetime. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>handle</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The opened instance handle, if failed will be set to NULL. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>0 on success or negative error value on failure. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
